Usage instructions:

You need to get the python-bugzilla library:
$ git clone git://gitorious.org/opensuse/python-bugzilla.git -b suse

You also need osc:
# zypper in osc

Then, use the tool from the parent folder of where you have the repos cloned:
$ PYTHONPATH=python-bugzilla/:suse_bug_reporter/ suse_bug_reporter/bin/susebugreporter.py 


For testing:
Install python-nose (zypper in python-nose) and then just do:
$ PYTHONPATH=python-bugzilla/:suse_bug_reporter/ nosetests -w suse_bug_reporter/tests/

